That particular realm has a shocking lack of archers(compared to the others).<br>
It is therefore somewhat obvious that they are at a BIG disadvantage when<br>
facing say 9 Rangers. I daresay they would be gunned down quickly.<br>
However why is this 'bad'?  Obviously because they are not doing the killing.<br>
I must assert that I suspect the other side would say it was 'good'<br>
