to the people running the game. Beware Varixx, that is an obvious ploy.<br>
If you think the designers dont know that, you are greatly mistaken.<br>
They are MORE than aware.<br>
Nothing would give me greater pleasure than running over you in a faction fight.<br>
Fate is inscrutable, only time can tell.<br>
